title: Wednesday Sector Leaders: Precious Metals, Medical Instruments & Supplies - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, precious metals shares were relative leaders, up on the day by about 2.3%. Leading the group were shares of Alexco Resource, up about 6.3% and shares of Golden Star Resources up about 5.8% on the day.    makeArticleAd();  Also showing relative strength are medical instruments & supplies shares, up on the day by about 2% as a group, led by T2 Biosystems, trading up by about 58% and Establishment Labs Holdings, trading up by about 8.2% on Wednesday.
